1. *Adresu* mi je dao njegov prijatelj. (He gave me his address.) 
2. *Adresu* je trebalo da mi dostave preko pošte. (They were supposed to deliver the address to me via post.)
3. *Adresu* sam dobila u pismu. (I got the address in a letter.)
4. Pronašao sam *adresu* na internetu. (I found the address on the internet.)
5. *Adresu* je trebalo da navede na papiru. (It was necessary to indicate the address on paper.)
6. Ko ima *adresu* tvoje bake? (Who has your grandmother's address?)